init_text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: the most important things students should learn in school are the three Rs: Reading, Writing and Arithmetic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know I use it everyday!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We write texts on them every day.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know that there are many other things that students should learn in school, but these are the most important.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I know that I have learned many things in school that I will never use in my life.
